{"tid":41612,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳WhatsApp推訊息撤回","createTime":"2016-12-16T04:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T18:43:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7733fa7265ed7a1ac7895cc112e21169b8e89bb","tid":41612,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19866902&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19866902%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161216&d=8su28JN39u2ivKGf5Dmse3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ca03a90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19866902%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161216&h=9ce72690\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19866902&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161216</a><br />\n<br />\n傳WhatsApp推訊息撤回<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■近年不斷增加新功能的WhatsApp，最近傳出將會推出「訊息撤回」功能。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】不少人倚賴WhatsApp作溝通平台，但只要輕輕觸一下「Send」，發出去訊息，有如潑出去的水，覆水難收。不過，近年不斷增加新功能的WhatsApp，最新傳出將會推出「訊息撤回」（Revoke）功能，用家發出訊息後覺得後悔、或誤發至錯誤目標，仍然有得自救！<br />\n<br />\n根據追蹤WhatsApp測試版消息之Twitter賬號WABetaInfo指出，最新WhatsApp iOS測試版本2.17.1.869上，驚現「訊息撤回」（Revoke）功能！此表示，用家只要長按已發出之訊息，再按「Revoke」，有關訊息將會於對話中消失，任何人都不會再有機會查閱。WABetaInfo更指，即使該訊息已被查閱變「雙藍剔」，發送人都一樣可以「撤回」；此功能同時適用於相片同影片。另外，WABetaInfo又透露，WhatsApp亦正開發「訊息修改」功能。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於上述功能仍在測試當中，更多詳細資料，如會否設有「訊息冷靜期」，即用家只可撤回幾多分鐘前的訊息；及新功能何時推出等，均有待官方進一步公佈。<br />\n<br />\n微信可撤兩分鐘內訊息事實上，微信（WeChat）早於2014年就已推出相同功能，並限制用家只能撤回兩分鐘內訊息。通常微信訊息撤回後，會收到一條提示：「對方撤回了一條消息」。相信WhatsApp的「訊息撤回」功能，會與微信相同，同樣會有類似的提示。<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;歐陸嘉年華今開幕　部份機動遊戲未有牌<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;政府申DQ四議員　明年2月審"},{"pid":"950d10a48e26e517043664c95482c3aa960b6aa1","tid":41612,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"姐夫有救"},{"pid":"452dc20cfbf2054abd6b86fd62aaac264712e339","tid":41612,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"一早應該要有啦, send 錯group 真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70789b369f251af8fc2bde4c82e3eb01b8d366f9","tid":41612,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"咁我同ex d 對話咪比人删曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7400655837bf29333990f954b3dbcd83b6ab45","tid":41612,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"whatsapp講完嘢咪可以反口反得一乾二淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2e089e7f959c91128ce781f6629ff6555218f4","tid":41612,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"ON9功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咗邊有得收返架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc232887097796ca32b59fb70619e0bf1b932dda","tid":41612,"uid":31875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐夫有救</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f106dfac3b472533c9a5c3ff429fc61dd77efa24","tid":41612,"uid":11442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姐夫有救</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正過呀妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b49e387b7d9de3c56b18aa61c5c3375760fee8","tid":41612,"uid":8042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>姐夫有救</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/as